<p>This is nothing newâ€“itâ€™s particularly popular in the entrepreneurial and goal-setting circles. Some people call them decision journals, scientists have their Scientific Process, and even the Navy Seals have their own: AARs (After Action Reviews).<span class="cite"><a href="#note-1" name="back-1">1</a></span></p>

<p>All my projects now start with a brief and end with a review:</p>

