        <li>What do we expect to happen?</li>
        <li>What does success look like?</li>
        </ol>
    <hr class="--small" /></td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td><strong>Review</strong>
    <br />
        <ol>
        <li>What was the outcome?</li>
        <li>Was my hypothesis correct?</li>
        <li>What did we learn for next time?</li>
        </ol>
    </td>
</tr>
</table>

